Package: growthcurve
Title: Growth Curve Analysis Shiny Application
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Jordan", "Barrows", email = "jordan.m.barrows@gmail.com", 
                   role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive Shiny application for analyzing microbial growth curves
    from plate reader and oCelloscope instruments. Provides tools for single-plate
    analysis, batch processing, and results aggregation with interactive visualization
    and quality control flagging.
